{"tid":2079731,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"美制裁或禁運高科技產品，最壞情況：香港冇Router賣","createTime":"2020-06-26T03:44:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T10:21:56.000Z","uid":109923,"like":23,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"0afea63029d9ebae070160626df6ee9d89705f43","tid":2079731,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T03:44:42.000Z","msg":"現今加密技術對多個行業，特別是互聯網尤其重要。資訊科技界立法會議員莫乃光表示，不少商用路由器核心加密技術，專利都屬於美國公司，電訊機構、大企業內部網絡等都廣泛採用，若落實制裁相信全部首當其衝，「講到國家安全，最好就係乜都睇到你啲嘢，但係畀你加咗密咁我即係睇唔到，佢哋就會對呢啲技術出口比較敏感。」<br />\n<br />\n香港互聯網服務供應商協會主席葉旭暉指出，設置網絡工程最重要是訊息的保安，關鍵取決於路由器或交換器中加密軟件是否可靠，無論是商用還是免費開源程式資料庫，技術核心大多屬於美國，如制裁對行業影響深遠，「起碼就入唔到router先囉，要用華為先啦。」<br />\n<br />\n全文請click link：<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200626/BW6KODKTJQGS4XDZMVG7XNWKDE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200626%2FBW6KODKTJQGS4XDZMVG7XNWKDE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=b6PV2mHT5tDC6%2Fq4CXK2Smvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=ce7e2123\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200626%2FBW6KODKTJQGS4XDZMVG7XNWKDE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=ac67eb9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200626/BW6KODKTJQGS4XDZMVG7XNWKDE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"f3d73e13cc3fc0474c4463d8148f40b9b33344d1","tid":2079731,"uid":54092,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0afea63029d9ebae070160626df6ee9d89705f43","tid":2079731,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T03:44:42.000Z","msg":"現今加密技術對多個行業，特別是互聯網尤其重要。資訊科技界立法會議員莫乃光表示，不少商用路由器核心加密技術，專利都屬